---
interface Props {
  show?: boolean;
}

const { show = false } = Astro.props;
---

<div 
  id="bulkActions" 
  class={`fixed bottom-6 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg px-6 py-4 transition-all duration-200 ${
    show ? 'opacity-100 translate-y-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-y-2 pointer-events-none'
  }`}
>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
    <span id="selectedCount" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">
      0 game được chọn
    </span>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <button 
        id="bulkDeleteBtn"
        class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Xóa đã chọn
      </button>
      <button 
        id="clearSelection"
        class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Bỏ chọn
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Bulk Delete Confirmation Modal -->
<div id="bulkDeleteModal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 z-50 hidden items-center justify-center">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl max-w-md w-full mx-4 p-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Xác nhận xóa games</h3>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
      Bạn có chắc chắn muốn xóa <span id="bulkDeleteCount" class="font-medium text-red-600"></span> game(s) đã chọn?
    </p>
    
    <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-3 mb-6">
      <p class="text-sm text-red-800">
        <strong>Cảnh báo:</strong> Hành động này không thể hoàn tác. Tất cả dữ liệu game sẽ bị xóa vĩnh viễn.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div id="bulkDeleteGamesList" class="max-h-32 overflow-y-auto mb-6 space-y-1">
      <!-- Games list will be populated here -->
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
      <button id="cancelBulkDelete" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg transition-colors">Hủy</button>
      <button id="confirmBulkDelete" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 rounded-lg transition-colors">Xác nhận xóa</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>